<p xid="561" props="margin-top:0.0000in; margin-left:0.0000in; text-indent:0.0000in; margin-bottom:0.0000in; line-height:1.0000; text-align:justify; margin-right:0.0000in"><c props="font-weight:normal; color:#000000; font-family:TibetanMachineNormalType 1; font-size:30pt; font-style:normal">[s]/དེ-ཕྱིར-བདག-གཞན-བརྗེ-བའི-རྣལ-འབྱོར-ལ/</c></p>
