<p xid="563" props="margin-top:0.0000in; margin-left:0.0000in; text-indent:0.0000in; margin-bottom:0.0000in; line-height:1.0000; text-align:justify; margin-right:0.0000in"><c props="font-weight:normal; color:#000000; font-family:PalatinoDiaRomanType 1; font-size:12pt; font-style:normal">Cherishing myself alone is the door to every trouble,</c></p>
<p xid="564" props="margin-top:0.0000in; margin-left:0.0000in; text-indent:0.0000in; margin-bottom:0.0000in; line-height:1.0000; text-align:justify; margin-right:0.0000in"><c props="font-weight:normal; color:#000000; font-family:PalatinoDiaRomanType 1; font-size:12pt; font-style:normal">Cherishing my mothers the door to every spiritual quality;</c></p>
<p xid="565" props="margin-top:0.0000in; margin-left:0.0000in; text-indent:0.0000in; margin-bottom:0.0000in; line-height:1.0000; text-align:justify; margin-right:0.0000in"><c props="font-weight:normal; color:#000000; font-family:PalatinoDiaRomanType 1; font-size:12pt; font-style:normal">Please give me Your blessing then to make the practice of exchanging</c></p>
<p xid="566" props="margin-top:0.0000in; margin-left:0.0000in; text-indent:0.0000in; margin-bottom:0.0000in; line-height:1.0000; text-align:justify; margin-right:0.0000in"><c props="font-weight:normal; color:#000000; font-family:PalatinoDiaRomanType 1; font-size:12pt; font-style:normal">Myself and others the very heart of all my spiritual life.</c></p>
<p xid="567" props="margin-top:0.0000in; margin-left:0.0000in; text-indent:0.0000in; margin-bottom:0.0000in; line-height:1.0000; text-align:justify; margin-right:0.0000in"></p>
