<p xid="580" props="margin-top:0.0000in; margin-left:0.0000in; text-indent:0.0000in; margin-bottom:0.0000in; line-height:1.0000; text-align:justify; margin-right:0.0000in"><c props="font-weight:bold; color:#000000; font-family:PalatinoDiaRomanType 1; font-size:12pt; font-style:normal">Give me your blessing please so all the pain of mother beings,</c></p>
